node.text:
Sheep tribute: Ben Jackson, a sheep farmer stuck in lockdown in New South Wales, was unable to attend his aunt Deb's funeral. So he decided to honor her memory by creating a heart made from sheep that could be seen from heaven. 🙏🏽 ❤️ 🐑
Video by: guyrajack on Twitter.
Music by: Paul Simon
Via: @earthfocus
